---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Ted Goas
description: An Eleventy starter with modern tooling, Tailwind CSS and PurgeCSS
---
<div class="max-w-4xl bg-white mx-auto text-xl pt-8 my-16 md:rounded-lg shadow-2xl flex items-end">
	    
    <section class="-ml-16 lg:m-0">
		<h1 class="text-6xl text-blue-900 mb-8">Tai11s</h1>
		<p class=" leading-normal">
			This is an <a href="https://11ty.io">Eleventy</a> starter boilerplate with a <a href="/blog">blog</a> and:
		</p>
		<ul class="list my-8 px-8">
			<li>Tailwind CSS</li>
			<li>Sass</li>
			<li>Webpack</li>
			<li>Babel</li>
			<li>PostCSS</li>
			<li>CSS Nano</li>
			<li>Lightserver</li>
			<li>Autoprefixer</li>
		</ul>

		<ul>
			{%- for post in collections.blog | reverse -%}
			  <li>
				<h3><a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a> | {{ post.date }}</h3>
				{% if post.data.excerpt %}
				  <p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
				{% endif %}
			  </li>
			{%- endfor -%}
		</ul>
    </section> 

</div>
